    "description": "「让史莱姆控制人类，替你打仗！」<br>这是一款让你意想不到的战棋游戏。<br><br>你可以指挥史莱姆。<br>没错。最弱小的怪物，史莱姆。<br>不，它们在这个游戏中也没有变得更强。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171500/extras/2cf922bb3dbb5fe75d632841ca4c58ba.poster.avif?t=1725289183\" width=620 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171500/extras/2cf922bb3dbb5fe75d632841ca4c58ba.webm?t=1725289183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171500/extras/2cf922bb3dbb5fe75d632841ca4c58ba.mp4?t=1725289183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>但如果它们有附身人类的能力呢？<br><br>控制强大骑士和魔法师的身体来对抗人类敌人！<br>还有恶魔来找麻烦，所以局面可能会有点混乱。<br>恶魔无法被控制，但如果你利用周围的人类……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171500/extras/7f0e6e32dd2aa45dcc704fdb147a3ad5.poster.avif?t=1725289183\" width=620 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171500/extras/7f0e6e32dd2aa45dcc704fdb147a3ad5.webm?t=1725289183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171500/extras/7f0e6e32dd2aa45dcc704fdb147a3ad5.mp4?t=1725289183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在游戏中能看到各种类型的史莱姆、人类和恶魔。<br>有超过20种类型的史莱姆可供指挥，每种史莱姆都有其独特的能力。传送、分裂，甚至还有一种史莱姆可以融化敌人的装备！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171500/extras/e825ce409cbd7c0ed5b484078403ef84.poster.avif?t=1725289183\" width=620 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171500/extras/e825ce409cbd7c0ed5b484078403ef84.webm?t=1725289183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171500/extras/e825ce409cbd7c0ed5b484078403ef84.mp4?t=1725289183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>该占领哪个身体？该用什么方式战斗？<br>发掘无限的可能性！<br>史莱姆占领人类时，人类总会试图拯救他们的朋友。这也可以成为你战略的一部分。<br>使用道具将你的史莱姆变成不同类型，帮助你面对游戏后期更具挑战性的战斗。<br><br>发挥你的智慧，帮助史莱姆占领全世界！",
